headline: Xcel Energy named one of the World’s Most Ethical Companies for sixth consecutive year
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, March 24, 2025--For a sixth consecutive year, Xcel Energy has been named a World’s Most Ethical Companies® honoree by Ethisphere.
